high_descs: Turn around until you see the blue bin next to the fridge, go over to the blue bin next to the fridge and face the wooden rack from the side.
Pick up the potato in the blue bin.
There is a microwave on the counter left of the fridge, bring the potato over to the microwave left of the fridge.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the heated potato to the fridge, left of the mike.
Put the heated potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to stand in front of the blue trash can next to the fridge.

Move over to the right and face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the potato out and shut the door again.
Move back to the left and face the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge and shut the door.
